      • findFirst1ByStatusOrderByTimeNewAsc

        java.util.List<Dmer> findFirst1ByStatusOrderByTimeNewAsc(Dmer.Status status)
        For all Dmer entities with a specified status, retrieves the one with the earliest timeNew value. This thus implements a FIFO queue.
        Parameters:
        status - the desired Dmer Status
        Returns:
        a single member List containing the earliest Dmer of the specified status
